Ursa Major/DarkMouse

Ursa Major sees the ion disks come flying at her. She dodges 2 of them but 
the third hits her in the leg slicing it open.  She screams out in pain.  
The plasma blasts send her fliying into a tree, which she cracks in half 
from the impact, and lands at the base of the tree. The stinger missles hit 
her dead on.  She is heavily damaged.  She finds enough strength to stand 
and she walks over to DarkMouse.  She covers DarkMouses body with her as the 
heat seaking missles hit.  DarkMouse is not further damaged as Ursa Major 
took the hit from the missles.  Ursa Major collapses ontop of DarkMouse.  
Ursa Major's spark flutters......and gives out.  Ursa Major is dead.

DarkMouse is barely alive while under the wait of Ursa Major's body.



Please put Ursa Major on the deceased list as killed by Manterror,  Counter 
Punch, Bumblebee.
